import { Form, Button, Row, Col, Accordion } from 'react-bootstrap'; import React, { useEffect, useState }from 'react'; import './App.css'; function Search() { var [genre, genre_change] = useState(['드라마', 'SF/판타지', '공포', '로맨스', '모험', '스릴러', '범죄/느와르', '다큐멘터리', '코미디', '가족', '미스터리/서스펜스', '전쟁', '애니메이션', '뮤지컬', '액션/무협', '에로', '영화음악', '기타']) return (
Title Search Detail { genre.map(function(g, i ){ return }) }
) } export default Search;
